  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we want to explore and verify whether infusing RST knowledge into LoRA can improve the performance of long document summarization.",
    "To answer this question, this paper will propose, introduce, and integrate four RST structure variants to guide the training of LoRA.",
    "These variants include (i) binary (ii) probability RST distribution, both with (w) and without(w/o) relation labels.",
    "In summary, our contributions are as follows:",
    "• We introduce a method for injecting discourse knowledge into the training of the LoRA model."
